				<h2>Automated Upsell System</h2>
				<p>Upselling is offering customers a premium version or upgrade of what they already bought. When done right, it increases revenue while improving customer satisfaction.</p>

				<h3>Smart Upsell Triggers</h3>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Usage-Based</strong> - When customers hit limits or need more capacity</li>
					<li><strong>Time-Based</strong> - After proving value during trial or initial period</li>
					<li><strong>Success-Based</strong> - When customers achieve milestones that indicate readiness</li>
					<li><strong>Behavior-Based</strong> - When actions suggest they need premium features</li>
				</ul>

				<h3>Upsell Automation Examples</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>SaaS: Free ‚Üí Pro ‚Üí Enterprise based on usage and team size</li>
					<li>Services: One-time ‚Üí Retainer based on results achieved</li>
					<li>E-commerce: Standard ‚Üí Premium products based on satisfaction</li>
					<li>Membership: Basic ‚Üí VIP based on engagement level</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Automated Cross-Sell Strategies</h2>
				<p>Cross-selling is offering complementary products that enhance what customers already bought.</p>

				<h3>Cross-Sell Techniques</h3>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Bundle Recommendations</strong> - "Customers who bought X also bought Y"</li>
					<li><strong>Post-Purchase Sequences</strong> - Follow-up emails with relevant add-ons</li>
					<li><strong>Usage-Triggered Offers</strong> - Suggest products based on how they use existing ones</li>
					<li><strong>Lifecycle-Based Offers</strong> - Right product at right stage of journey</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Automated Referral System</h2>
				<p>Your happiest customers are your best marketers‚Äîif you make it easy for them to refer others.</p>

				<h3>Referral Automation Components</h3>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Timing</strong> - Ask for referrals after moments of peak satisfaction</li>
					<li><strong>Incentives</strong> - Reward both referrer and referred (double-sided rewards work best)</li>
					<li><strong>Simplicity</strong> - One-click sharing with pre-written messages</li>
					<li><strong>Tracking</strong> - Automated tracking and reward distribution</li>
					<li><strong>Follow-Up</strong> - Remind customers who haven't referred yet</li>
				</ul>

				<h3>When to Ask for Referrals (Automated Triggers)</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>After successful onboarding completion</li>
					<li>Following positive support interaction</li>
					<li>When customer achieves a goal using your product</li>
					<li>After they give you high satisfaction rating</li>
					<li>At renewal time when they're re-committing</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Automated Review Generation</h2>
