				<h3>Review Automation Strategy</h3>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Identify Promoters</strong> - Use NPS or satisfaction scores to find happy customers</li>
					<li><strong>Perfect Timing</strong> - Ask right after a positive experience</li>
					<li><strong>Multiple Platforms</strong> - Make it easy to review on Google, Facebook, industry sites</li>
					<li><strong>Gentle Persistence</strong> - Follow up with non-responders (without being annoying)</li>
					<li><strong>Thank & Reward</strong> - Acknowledge customers who leave reviews</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>Customer Ascension System</h2>
				<p>A customer ascension system is a strategic path that moves customers from low-commitment offerings to high-value relationships.</p>

