					<li><strong>Entry Offer</strong> - Low-risk first purchase</li>
					<li><strong>Core Offer</strong> - Main product/service</li>
					<li><strong>Premium Offer</strong> - High-touch, high-value service</li>
					<li><strong>VIP/Partnership</strong> - Ongoing, strategic relationship</li>
				</ol>

				<h3>Ascension Automation</h3>
				<p>Automatically identify when customers are ready to move up the ladder and present the next offer:</p>
				<ul>
